## Basic Information


### Naming Convention
$APOGEE_REDUX/[APRED]/cal/[INSTRUMENT]/telluric/apTelluric-[CHIP]-[NUM].fits

### Releases
WORK

### Enviroments
APOGEE_REDUX

### Approximate Size
812 MB

### File Type
FITS

### Generated by Product
apogee_drp

### Is a VAC
False
